%global packname  GCAI.bias
%global packver   1.0
%global rlibdir   /usr/local/lib/R/library

Name:             R-CRAN-%{packname}
Version:          1.0
Release:          3%{?dist}%{?buildtag}
Summary:          Guided Correction Approach for Inherited bias (GCAI.bias)

License:          GPL (>= 2)
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel >= 2.10
Requires:         R-core >= 2.10
BuildArch:        noarch

%description
Many inherited biases and effects exists in RNA-seq due to both biological
and technical effects. We observed the biological variance of testing
target transcripts can influence the yield of sequencing reads, which
might indicate a resource competition existing in RNA-seq. We developed
this package to capture the bias depending on local sequence and perform
the correction of this type of bias by borrowing information from spike-in
measurement.

%prep
%setup -q -c -n %{packname}


